idiom_meaning("call it a day", "to stop working on something for now").
idiom_meaning("hit the nail on the head", "to describe exactly what is causing a situation or problem").
idiom_meaning("burn the midnight oil", "to work or study late into the night").
idiom_meaning("the last straw", "the final small problem that makes a situation unbearable").
idiom_meaning("speak of the devil", "said when a person you were just talking about appears").
